How to install Python 3 on redhat 7

 yum install -y epel-release
 yum install -y python36 python36-pip
 
 alias python='python3'#####this command is to use PY3 rather than the default PY2.7
 
 subscription-manager repos --enable rhel-7-server-optional-rpms \ --enable rhel-server-rhscl-7-rpms #### subscription to rpms
 
